<input id="roof" value="<%= quotation.rows.find(r => r.title === 'Roof Type')?.values[0] || 'Flat Roof' %>" /></div><div class="toolbar"><span>Live CRM quotation · all calculations update instantly</span><div class="pages" id="nav"></div></div><div class="book">
<section class="page cover active"><div class="coverHero"><div class="logo" style="margin-bottom:15px"><img src="data:image/png;base64,<%= logoBase64 %>" alt="SMS ENTERPRISE" style="max-height: 38px;" /></div><div class="eyebrow">Residential solar EPC proposal</div><h1>Power your home with sunshine.</h1><div class="coverSub" id="coverSize">5 kW On-Grid Solar System</div></div><div class="coverInfo"><div><div class="kicker">Prepared exclusively for</div><h2 data-name><%= lead.fullName || "Customer" %></h2><p style="font-size: 16px; font-weight: 600"><%= lead.contact || "" %></p><p class="lead">A premium, end-to-end clean-energy solution engineered for long-term savings.</p></div><div class="meta"><span id="today"></span><br>Prepared by <b data-exec><%= lead.assignName || "Sales Executive" %></b><br/><div style="font-size: 15px; font-weight: 800; margin-top:2px; color:var(--ink)"><%= lead.assignContact || "" %></div></div></div></section>
<section class="page"><div class="kicker">01 · Company profile</div><h2>A solar partner built around certainty.</h2><p class="lead" style="max-width:100%; margin-bottom:20px; line-height:1.8; text-align:justify; font-size:15px;">SMS Enterprise is a leading provider of residential solar solutions, helping homeowners switch to clean, reliable, and cost-effective energy. We offer complete turnkey services, including consultation, customized system design, professional installation, and dedicated after-sales support. Using premium-quality solar components and skilled workmanship, we ensure maximum efficiency and long-term performance. Our mission is to reduce electricity costs while promoting a sustainable and eco-friendly lifestyle. With a strong focus on quality, trust, and customer satisfaction, SMS Enterprise is your reliable partner for powering homes with solar energy.</p><div class="kpis" style="grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr); margin-bottom: 25px;"><div class="kpi purple"><small>Residential</small><b style="font-size:22px">2000+</b><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--mut);">Projects</span></div><div class="kpi blue"><small>Commercial</small><b style="font-size:22px">50+</b><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--mut);">Projects</span></div><div class="kpi green"><small>Total Capacity</small><b style="font-size:22px">15+ MW</b><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--mut);">Installed</span></div><div class="kpi"><small>Experience</small><b style="font-size:22px">10+ Yrs</b><span style="font-size:10px;color:var(--mut);">In Solar EPC</span></div></div><hr style="border:0;border-top:1px dashed #e8dfea;margin:20px 0"/><div class="kicker">02 · Why go solar</div><h2>A smarter bill. A lighter footprint.</h2><div class="kpis" style="grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr; max-width: 500px;"><div class="kpi green"><small>Monthly saving</small><b data-saving>₹5,400</b></div><div class="kpi"><small>Payback</small><b data-payback>3.8 yrs</b></div></div><hr style="border:0;border-top:1px dashed #e8dfea;margin:20px 0"/><div class="kicker">03 · Proposed system</div><h2>Designed for <span data-name><%= lead.fullName || "Customer" %></span>.</h2><div class="twocol"><div class="offer"><div class="row"><span>System size</span><b data-size>5 kW</b></div><div class="row"><span>Solar module</span><b data-module><%= quotation.solarModule || "-" %></b></div><div class="row"><span>Module quantity</span><b data-panels>10 × 550 W</b></div><div class="row"><span>Inverter</span><b data-inverter><%= quotation.inverter || "-" %></b></div><div class="row"><span>Roof / area</span><b data-area>Flat · 500 sq ft</b></div></div><div class="panel"><h3>Expected performance</h3><div class="kpis" style="grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr; margin-top:10px; margin-bottom:0;"><div class="kpi blue"><small>Daily units</small><b data-daily>22.5</b></div><div class="kpi blue"><small>Monthly units</small><b data-monthly>675</b></div><div class="kpi"><small>Annual units</small><b data-annual>8,213</b></div><div class="kpi"><small>25-year generation</small><b data-gen25>174k</b></div></div></div></div><div class="footer"><span><b>SMS ENTERPRISE</b></span><span>02</span></div></section>
<section class="page"><div class="kicker">04 · Technical specifications</div><h2>Quality in every connection.</h2>

<div class="brand-category">
